    "id": "v35"
  }, "v35"), mdx("p", null, "r\u1ED3i tuy\xEAn b\u1ED1, 'T\xF4i v\xF4 t\u1ED9i. Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF kh\xF4ng n\u1ED5i th\u1ECBnh n\u1ED9 c\xF9ng t\xF4i \u0111\xE2u.' Nh\u01B0ng ta s\u1EBD k\u1EBFt t\u1ED9i ng\u01B0\u01A1i v\xEC n\xF3i d\u1ED1i, V\xEC ng\u01B0\u01A1i b\u1EA3o, 'T\xF4i c\xF3 ph\u1EA1m t\u1ED9i \u0111\xE2u.' "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v36"
  }, "v36"), mdx("p", null, "Th\u1EADt qu\xE1 d\u1EC5 cho c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111\u1ED5i \xFD. \u0110\u1EBFn n\u1ED7i Ai-c\u1EADp c\u0169ng nh\u01B0 A-xy-ri \u0111\u1EC1u l\xE0m nh\u1EE5c ng\u01B0\u01A1i. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v37"
  }, "v37"), mdx("p", null, "Cu\u1ED1i c\xF9ng ng\u01B0\u01A1i s\u1EBD r\u1EDDi n\u01A1i \u0111\xF3 hai tay ch\u1EAFp tr\xEAn \u0111\u1EA7u nh\u01B0 t\xF9 binh. Ng\u01B0\u01A1i tin c\u1EADy c\xE1c n\u01B0\u1EDBc \u0111\xF3, nh\u01B0ng ch\xFAng ch\u1EB3ng gi\xFAp g\xEC \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c cho ng\u01B0\u01A1i, v\xEC CH\xDAA \u0111\xE3 t\u1EEB b\u1ECF ch\xFAng.\""), mdx("hr", null), mdx("p", null, "", mdx("a", {
